org.batfish.datamodel.acl

Class AclExplainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.acl.AclExplainer

  • public final class AclExplainer
extends Object
    Generate an explanation of the headerspace permitted by an IpAccessList. The explanation is a single AclLineMatchExpr in a simplified normal form. First we normalize to something analogous to Disjunctive Normal Form, then simplify further if possible.
